            "draft_value": "* Supporting NASA SMD at $9 billion secures U.S. leadership against China's rapid expansion in space science and lunar exploration.\n* Direct investment in MD-6 includes $318,955 in recent obligations to local entities like CSP Enterprises, LLC and Amentum Services, Inc.\n* Every $1 of NASA funding returns $3 to the economy, driving growth for Maryland's specialized aerospace and innovation workforce.\n* Funding restores stability to the scientific community after FY2026 disruptions, protecting high-skilled jobs at district firms like Cryo Associates Inc.",
